# Core CPU Benchmarks

```@setup BENCH
# Load utilities
include(normpath(joinpath(@__DIR__, "..", "docutils", "utils.jl")))
```

!!! note
    - The linear solver is [MUMPS](https://github.com/JuliaSmoothOptimizers/MUMPS.jl) for CPU experiments and [CUDSS](https://github.com/exanauts/CUDSS.jl) for GPU experiments.
    - Below you can find Dolan–Moré performance profiles comparing solver–model combinations on the set of optimal control problems and grid sizes. For a detailed explanation of how to read these profiles, see the [Performance Profiles](@ref performance-profiles) page.

## Ubuntu Latest

This benchmark suite evaluates optimal control problems on a standard CPU platform using GitHub Actions runners.

